            <dt class="- topic/dt ">Rough container type</dt>
            <dd class="- topic/dd ">Finish edges are rough due to a dirty finish or blurred due to curvature of the crown
          finish.</dd>
         </dlentry>
      </dl>
      <dl id="dl_xhx_lcv_tcc" class="- topic/dl ">
