            <dt class="- topic/dt ">No Step container type</dt>
            <dd class="- topic/dd ">Improve Wire Edge or Overpress Finish detection on containers with no or very slight
          step downs. Only use this type after plant evaluation of tradeoffs against commercial ware
          loss.</dd>
